Package: com.pvzhdfix.nocrash
Name: PvZ HD No Crash
Depends: mobilesubstrate (>= 0.9.5000)
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: Prevents PvZ HD from crashing by blocking network checks.
 All ad SDKs and reachability checks are hooked to return
 "no connectivity" state, preventing crashes caused by
 dead/offline servers.
Maintainer: PvZHDFix
Author: PvZHDFix
Section: Tweaks
